message:
Hi, very helpful post. I am quite new to to .net programming and async / synchronus actions. I understand that if I call an async action from my synchronous button click action that this might cause deadlock as you explained. However, what if we would just do this with your example:

var jsonTask = GetJsonAsync(...);  
jsonTask.Wait();   
return jsonTask.Result.ToString();

Won't this solve it too? If I understand the problem correctly this should solve it right? If not, can you please elaborate why not? Thanks a lot!
